Kuhlaselwe isonto eKenya 2012-11-05 07:33 Nairobi - IRed Cross eKenya iveze ukuthi kulimale abantu abayishumi ngesikhathi kuhlaselwa ngebhomu ngesikhathi kuqhubeka inkonzo yamaphoyisa esontweni elisenyakatho nezwe. Ngokombiko weRed Cross, lokhu kuhlasela kwenzeke e-Utawala Interdenominational Church, edolobheni iGarissa. IKenya isihlaselwe wuhide lwezigameko ezibandakanya iziqhumane nokusolwa kuzo i-al-Shabaab, nokuyinhlangano yezihonga yaseSomali eyamaniswa ne-al-Qaeda. IGauteng iGauteng iyifundazwe zaseNingizimu Afrika. Isifundazwe esincane kodwa esinabantu abaningi abahlala kuso. Igama elithi Gauteng ngesisuthu lisho ukuthi Kwindawo yeGolide ngamafuphi iGoli. Abantu baseGoli noma Gauteng bakhuluma ulimu lwesizulu, isiNgisi, isiBhunu, isiSuthu nesiXhosa. iGoli liyisifundazwe esicebile eNingizimu Afrika futhi sihlobe ngamabhilidi amakhulukazi futhi nendawo yokuhwebela ikhona eGoli kuthiwa yi-Johannesburg Stock Exchange ise-Sandton kwelinye lamadolobha amahle kakhulu e-Afrika yonkana.
